content: I'm rather "meh" over this launcher. I was really hoping it would be an independent launcher but I understood before I installed it you need one of the listed launchers. I tried this with Total Launcher and Next Launcher.  This works best with Total Launcher, as stated in the description.  I couldn't create new short cuts or move old ones.. Also, I could not change the temperature from Celsius to Fahrenheit. (I don't use Celsius.) It took some getting used to to understand the interface.   In order to get the interface for Total Launcher, it is a different download.  Don't bother if you have Next Launcher. It looks absolutely awful on Next Launcher. I would change the background and get a notice that the app stopped. Annoying.  This program relies on other apps (Beautiful Widgets and an actual launcher app.) I didn't care too much for that, even though I did play around with those applications. I'm giving this application 2 stars because it's very very pretty, but it is not easily configurable. I really wanted to like it, but it's too convoluted. After response from developer, I'm glad I got my money back. I'm a developer and understand development. Don't insult your users.
replyContent: There is a huge update now, and included tutorial in the Total Launcher theme that covers many of the things you missed before. I'm happy to help you with support mail newstartrekapps@gmail.com. I never meant to talk down to you, I just assumed ignorance from the things you missed before. I wish TL had a complete tutorial, things are easy to miss.
